Release 0.2   22 July 2001
--------------------------

 * auto-cxx skeleton gets a better layout: new config directory
 * cxx: justmake collection is separated into interface and implementation
 * more automake like interfaces to justmake
 * better library handling and libtool invocation
 * better multiple library and program build support, with interdependencies
 * preliminary recursive make and cvs support
 * cxx/: small compatibility fixes for g++-3.0
 * misc. fixes
